Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.30,0:01:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，今天就上到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.74,0:01:48.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:51.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下週日是期待已久的模擬考
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.14,0:01:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家準備 OK 了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.84,0:01:57.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次的模擬考\N能夠清楚的了解上榜機率
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據考試的成績\N也有可能更改志願
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個考試非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.89,0:02:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考成績不好的同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.06,0:02:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次上課我會點你出來\N回答問題的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.13,0:02:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師，沒有人會因為那種事\N而感到困擾的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真叫人期待不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.34,0:02:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.21,0:02:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師再見
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.57,0:02:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清水老師真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.91,0:02:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過她的課蠻容易懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考就要到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.62,0:02:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.13,0:02:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天工作也請了假
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.53,0:02:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集中精神努力一天的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.61,0:02:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到你的自言自語了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個壞習慣得改掉才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:05.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說要集中精神\N是為了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.85,0:03:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.48,0:03:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我後天有模擬考
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想說明天打工請假
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.32,0:03:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力用功個一整天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.83,0:03:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工要請假…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.29,0:03:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考這麼難嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這是能了解\N自己目前能力的重要考試
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過補習班的課業好難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.94,0:03:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本趕不上進度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.94,0:03:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明趕不上課業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.38,0:03:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工回家後卻又馬上睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以最起碼在模擬考前一天\N明天一定要專心唸書
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長，請好好加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裕美
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.13,0:03:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺真是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，開店了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樂意之至
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:03:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.44,0:04:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，掉出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是補習班的課本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我唸書時非常重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.16,0:04:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,唸書的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.03,0:04:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,努力的去學習\N自己不懂或是新的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然講起來好像很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過卻是件很困難的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讀書，困難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明天要好好的唸書才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.98,0:04:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以ちぃ也要為我加油打氣喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.78,0:04:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.20,0:05:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，怎麼能認輸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.57,0:05:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.90,0:05:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.51,0:05:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行，不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.84,0:05:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得再努力一點才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,1，2，3，4\Nちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.99,0:06:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2，2，3，4\Nちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.90,0:06:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不能說是完全背熟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個就先看到這裡為止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.88,0:06:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是英文
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.89,0:06:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我最不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.26,0:06:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且課本又這麼厚
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.63,0:06:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這是這次最大的難關
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃晚飯前如果能看完一半的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.57,0:06:48.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天應該有辦法看完整本
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.11,0:06:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.94,0:06:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,respect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.58,0:06:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,respect 是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字典，字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.15,0:07:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.19,0:07:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，我不是在玩喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在找字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.06,0:07:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.76,0:07:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，從搬家到現在\N我好像都沒看到字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還沒開過的箱子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.10,0:07:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從這就可以看出\N我有多麼的刻意逃避英文
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.97,0:07:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字典，字典
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.24,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？難道…
