Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.25,0:07:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把字典放在家裡沒帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.85,0:07:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我到現在都沒發現啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.23,0:07:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣怎麼可能學得會英文嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.56,0:07:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天就要考試了\N我到底在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.79,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找到了，就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然，字典好貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.76,0:08:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這樣就能繼續唸書了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.67,0:08:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，英文也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.97,0:08:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.11,0:08:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.64,0:08:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是ちぃ第一次到書店來喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.98,0:08:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡叫作書店
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賣著各種書的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.49,0:08:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書的意思就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寫了許多東西的紙張
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.16,0:08:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,例如有趣或有用的東西之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.07,0:08:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫著很多東西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.37,0:09:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.07,0:09:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有很多書
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.74,0:09:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.85,0:09:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,だれもいない町（沒有人的小鎮）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳想要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.90,0:09:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好…好貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.23,0:09:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫冊要這麼貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.10,0:09:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.34,0:09:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果買了這個，字典就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是字典是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,模擬考…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.13,0:09:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給妳的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,禮…物？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.13,0:10:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我買給ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:04.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,買給ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.47,0:10:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與其我來教妳各種事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.10,0:10:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,書裡寫著更多有用的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候要說“謝謝”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（ちぃ真的好可愛）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.09,0:10:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要親熱麻煩請付錢後再親熱喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.63,0:10:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傷腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是妳第一次看書嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.24,0:10:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.15,0:10:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畫冊這種東西是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳看，這裡有圖畫對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.15,0:10:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.25,0:11:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後這裡是文章
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是透過圖畫與文章說故事的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，妳會看字嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.83,0:11:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個小鎮裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳看得懂字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.70,0:11:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好聰明啊，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.51,0:11:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那妳來讀讀看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.74,0:11:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個小鎮裡沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:32.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，本須和，你有在用功嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.45,0:11:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新保
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喔，搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.06,0:11:36.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們又在親熱了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.59,0:11:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.63,0:11:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真有閒情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.30,0:11:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還特地來激勵你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,激勵？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.17,0:11:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.41,0:11:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！加油！本須和！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.01,0:11:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！加油！本須和！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.78,0:11:58.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油！加油！考前準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，我得唸書才行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.55,0:12:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我連字典都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.39,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,字典怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我把字典放在家裡沒帶來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以沒辦法唸英文
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.53,0:12:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我的借你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.59,0:12:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過，那你怎麼唸書？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.43,0:12:18.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常都有做預習跟複習
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不需要臨時抱佛腳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.17,0:12:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本須和同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，竟然故意在我面前炫耀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.71,0:12:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，沒什麼，新保大爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.14,0:12:30.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼總之，到我房裡來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.85,0:12:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.22,0:12:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.58,0:12:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.90,0:12:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.77,0:12:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:02.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,respect 的意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔，就是尊敬的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.91,0:13:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這單字該怎麼用？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.32,0:13:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看，這裡這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.42,0:13:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當動詞與當名詞用時的差異
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.13,0:13:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果是形容詞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.13,0:13:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那當然就是 respectabIe
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.43,0:13:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那個小鎮裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.49,0:13:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.83,0:14:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.17,0:14:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從窗子望去也能看到燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是路上卻沒有半個人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從窗戶朝裡面望去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:13.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是卻跟“那個”在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也看了其他的房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是跟“那個”在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為跟“那個”在一起很愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.26,0:14:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比跟人在一起還愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以大家都不出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個小鎮裡沒有任何人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要出去旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去別的小鎮看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.65,0:14:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望有人能夠發現我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.55,0:14:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.02,0:15:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得只喜歡我一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.39,0:15:04.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.60,0:15:07.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我分手的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.67,0:15:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我還是想見到\N只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.41,0:15:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊這麼的想著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今天仍然朝著\N空無一人的小鎮走去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.16,0:15:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.13,0:15:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我…是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我好像懂了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.04,0:15:46.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的我自己會試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.47,0:15:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ！ Go ！ Let's Go ！本須和
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，絲茉茉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.05,0:16:00.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.42,0:16:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.96,0:16:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.39,0:16:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.79,0:16:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼了？ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.04,0:16:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.85,0:16:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂，ちぃ，妳沒事…吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從外表看來，似乎沒什麼異常
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.96,0:16:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟她是一台奇怪的電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.81,0:16:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說實話，我也完全不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼原因造成她這樣\N我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:00.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連你也不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.95,0:17:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暫時觀察一下情況
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.59,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒什麼應該就沒事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.99,0:17:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正現在運作得很正常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.96,0:17:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.29,0:17:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有你在，實在幫了我一個大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別掛在心上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.23,0:17:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我回去了，加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.53,0:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:28.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.84,0:17:30.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.41,0:17:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到還蠻有難度的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，妳全都讀完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.83,0:17:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.91,0:18:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺已經這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.98,0:18:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:09.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本來打算在晚餐前\N讀完半本課本的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果通通都沒讀到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.72,0:18:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.69,0:18:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼總是無法集中精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.87,0:18:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在才開始根本就來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.07,0:18:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英文果然還是沒救了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.12,0:18:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒關係了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.72,0:18:53.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.43,0:18:56.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣放棄了，對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.32,0:19:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.12,0:20:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，又有幹勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.90,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，麻煩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.64,0:20:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.47,0:20:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，我還能撐下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.21,0:20:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.94,0:20:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，麻煩一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.75,0:20:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.08,0:20:28.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，加油
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.09,0:20:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從後面往前傳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，累死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等要幹嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打工，打工
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.87,0:20:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，早安
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.21,0:20:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.65,0:21:03.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.16,0:21:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.36,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,考試結果雖然不能說很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但看樣子成績應該還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.07,0:21:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這都多虧有ちぃ在一旁幫我打氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的謝謝妳，ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.98,0:21:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，對了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等下次拿到打工的薪水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.02,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我再買點東西給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.89,0:21:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，期待
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.47,0:21:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,變得只喜歡我一個人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與我分手的時候了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.15,0:22:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使如此我還是想見到\N只屬於我的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.55,0:22:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一邊這麼的想著\N我今天仍然朝著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.79,0:22:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空無一人的小鎮走去…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.10,0:23:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秀樹，撞到頭了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.00,0:24:03.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.14,0:24:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是有一堆不做不行的事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.14,0:24:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋中都塞滿了東西
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腦袋塞滿？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.67,0:24:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.71,0:24:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,電費，瓦斯費，水費，房租，伙食費\N還有一堆有的沒的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.71,0:24:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ，擔心秀樹的腦袋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.35,0:24:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得好像內心受到劍傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.39,0:24:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chobits 下一回\N「ちぃ，虛弱了」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ちぃ她會不會感到頭痛啊？
